.el .ds Aq '
.TH antimony-info 1  "info " 
.SH NAME
antimony\-info \- Get information about profiles/features
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBantimony info\fR [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-feature\fR] [\fB\-\-diff\fR] [\fB\-s\fR|\fB\-\-system\fR] [\fB\-\-seccomp\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fINAME\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Get information about profiles/features
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-feature\fR
Target the feature set rather than the profile set
.TP
\fB\-\-diff\fR
Display the difference between system and user profiles
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-system\fR
Target the system set rather than the user set
.TP
\fB\-\-seccomp\fR
Display SECCOMP data. Overrides \-\-feature, \-\-system, and \-\-diff
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fINAME\fR]
The object to display information on. Default to everything
